00:42:06.876 --> 00:42:10.820
And at the same time, going into
my junior year where at

00:42:10.820 --> 00:42:14.250
that point I was drawing and
designing clothes, doing

00:42:14.250 --> 00:42:18.190
theater, making music,
skateboarding, BMXing.

00:42:18.190 --> 00:42:21.600
I was just all over the place in
everything I wanted to do.

00:42:21.600 --> 00:42:26.210
So to gain a scholarship by
pretty much singing for the

00:42:26.210 --> 00:42:26.640
most part--

00:42:26.640 --> 00:42:28.390
I had to do other things
in the pageant--

00:42:28.390 --> 00:42:32.800
it really said, Mom and Dad, I
think I'm not going to be a

00:42:32.800 --> 00:42:34.540
