00:45:40.640 --> 00:45:43.750
I literally can't make
it to class.

00:45:43.750 --> 00:45:44.740
I can't do this.

00:45:44.740 --> 00:45:46.670
So I took off like two years.

00:45:46.670 --> 00:45:48.430
And then the Warner Brothers
situation didn't work out.

00:45:48.430 --> 00:45:49.260
I went to Ireland.

00:45:49.260 --> 00:45:51.130
An the Ireland situation
