00:46:00.120 --> 00:46:02.506
my scholarship back.

00:46:02.506 --> 00:46:05.120
I'll get straight
A's, I promise.

00:46:05.120 --> 00:46:09.850
And amazingly, I went back.

00:46:09.850 --> 00:46:11.890
But it was crazy, because
I went back.

00:46:11.890 --> 00:46:14.730
And it was like, (WHISPERS) oh,
there's that kid that had

00:46:14.730 --> 00:46:15.730
that record deal.

00:46:15.730 --> 00:46:17.800
Like the whispers walking
across the yard like,

00:46:17.800 --> 00:46:20.426
(WHISPERS) oh, that's the kid
that fell off [INAUDIBLE]

00:46:20.426 --> 00:46:20.902
video.

00:46:20.902 --> 00:46:22.290
That was a long time ago.

00:46:22.290 --> 00:46:25.070
I wonder if he still
got money.

00:46:25.070 --> 00:46:27.920
So like the humbleness
of like--

00:46:27.920 --> 00:46:31.310
it made me a better student, a
