00:46:45.830 --> 00:46:48.340
I didn't know how to
handle everything.

00:46:48.340 --> 00:46:49.390
So I had to go back.

00:46:49.390 --> 00:46:52.190
And going back to school and
graduating was like the

00:46:52.190 --> 00:46:54.410
